segue_dave.line: The song "Goodbye Garageland" is dedicated to The Clash, and the same song is also dedicated to Joe Strummer...
segue_dave.explanation: The Clash is dedicated to the song Goodbye Garageland and Joe Strummer is dedicated to the song Goodbye Garageland
